:: Create Meaningful Projects {"position":"700,700","size":"100,100"}
You’ve always loved video games—they’ve been a constant source of joy and inspiration in your life. You admire how they combine creativity, storytelling, and technical skill to create immersive experiences. Deep down, you’ve always wanted to learn how to create them, to be a part of bringing that magic to life. So, to reignite your passion for Computer Science, you decide to start small: coding a simple clone of Pong.


