:: Push Through, stick with the current degree {"position":"900,500","size":"100,100"}
You decide to stick with Computer Science, but not just to finish your degree—you want to rediscover why you started. The path ahead feels daunting, but the choice to stay fills you with determination. You realize that to break out of the lull, you need to take proactive steps to reignite your passion and find new purpose. Two ideas come to mind immediately: creating meaningful projects that excite you and building a network of like-minded peers and mentors who can inspire and guide you. 

